an Eastercon can use, which is unusual for a hotel.

77
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:45,020
The other thing that had changed in between our two more recent visits is that they'd had the furries,

78
00:06:45,020 --> 00:06:52,440
I think a couple of times. And I think the furries are more or less exactly like the Eastercon,

79
